<td><i>This  article  is a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/stub" class="extiw" title="wikipedia:stub">stub</a>.  <a href="Contact" title="Contact">Editors</a> can help the Chinese Grammar Wiki by <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=Expressing_%22always_previously%22_with_%22xianglai%22&amp;action=edit">expanding it</a>.</i><div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar mini" style="position:absolute; right:15px; font-size:smaller; display:none;"><ul><li class="nv-view"><a href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/chinese/grammar/Template:Stub" title="Template:Stub"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li><li class="nv-talk"><a href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=Template_talk:Stub&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Template talk:Stub (page does not exist)"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">t</span></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=Template:Stub&amp;action=edit"><span title="Edit this template" style="">e</span></a></li></ul></div></td>
</tr></tbody></table>
<p>向来 (xiànglái) is pretty much the <a href="&quot;Never&quot;_with_&quot;conglai&quot;" class="mw-redirect" title="&quot;Never&quot; with &quot;conglai&quot;">same as 从来</a>, except that 从来 is almost always used with negation (sentences with 不 or 没）.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="ASGDU0XL#Structure"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="ASGDU0XL#Examples"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Examples</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="ASGDU0XL#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="ASGDU0XL#Sources_and_further_reading"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Sources and further reading</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="ASGDU0XL#Dictionaries"><span class="tocnumber">4.1</span> <span class="toctext">Dictionaries</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Structure">Structure</span></h2>
<p>向来 is used the same structure as 从来.You can use an optional 都 after the 向来.The basic meaning of 向来 is that something is always like that until the present. <a href="&quot;Since_the_beginning&quot;_with_&quot;yixiang&quot;" class="mw-redirect" title="&quot;Since the beginning&quot; with &quot;yixiang&quot;">一向</a> has the same meaning and structure as 向来。 
</p>
<div class="jiegou">
<p>Subject + 向来（都） + Verb/Verb Phrase
</p>
</div>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Examples">Examples</span></h2>
<div class="liju">
<ul><li>我 父母 <em>向来</em> 不 喜欢 我 跟 你们 一起 出去 玩儿。<span class="trans">My parents have always disliked me going out to play with you guys.</span></li>
<li>我 <em>向来</em> 努力，所以 我 每 一 次 考试 都 得 满分。<span class="trans">I have always pushed myself, so every time I take a test, I always get full marks.</span></li>
<li>那个 足球 队员 <em>一向</em> 被 称为 “金脚”，因为 他 踢 足球 踢 得 非常 好。<span class="trans">That soccer player is known as "Goldfoot" because he plays soccer really well.</span></li></ul>
</div>
